        <h2>Partial webpage to PDF</h2>
        <p>
            A part of a webpage can be converted to PDF based on the HTML tag ID.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a class="btn btn-default" href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301950">Learn more &raquo;</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

